//Using input statement//

name = input("What is your name?")
print(name)
Output:What is your name? Sihi

//Without input statement//

name = "Sihi"
print(name)
Output:Sihi

//Variables can be changed accordingly,variables can be varied//

name = "Sihi"
print(name)
name = "Gopal"
print(name)

Output:Sihi
       Gopal
